2025-12-31 21:25:13,565 - MetaFlow.llm.client - INFO - Execute tool write_file with args: {'path': 'core/powerups/shield.py', 'content': 'from core.effect_interface import EffectInterface\nfrom core.snake import Snake\nimport threading\n\nclass Shield(EffectInterface):\n    """\n    Power-up effect: Allows the snake to pass through walls for a limited time.\n    """\n\n    def __init__(self, duration: int = 5):\n        """\n        Initializes the Shield effect with a specified duration.\n\n        :param duration: Duration (in seconds) for which the effect lasts.\n        """\n        self.duration = duration\n\n    def apply(self, snake: Snake) -> None:\n        """\n        Allows the snake to pass through walls for a limited time.\n\n        :param snake: The Snake instance to which the effect is applied.\n        """\n        # Enable wall passing for the snake\n        snake.wall_pass = True\n\n        # Create a timer to disable the effect after the duration\n        def disable_effect():\n            snake.wall_pass = False\n\n        timer = threading.Timer(self.duration, disable_effect)\n        timer.start()'}
