2025-12-31 21:26:16,813 - MetaFlow.llm.client - INFO - Execute tool write_file with args: {'path': 'core/movement.py', 'content': 'from typing import Tuple\n\nclass Movement:\n    def change_direction(self, current_direction: Tuple[int, int], new_direction: Tuple[int, int]) -> Tuple[int, int]:\n        """\n        Changes the snake\'s direction, ensuring it does not reverse.\n\n        Parameters:\n        current_direction (Tuple[int, int]): Current direction of the snake (dx, dy).\n        new_direction (Tuple[int, int]): New direction of the snake (dx, dy).\n\n        Returns:\n        Tuple[int, int]: The updated direction of the snake.\n        """\n        # Ensure the new direction is not the reverse of the current direction\n        if (current_direction[0] + new_direction[0] == 0 and \n            current_direction[1] + new_direction[1] == 0):\n            # Snake cannot reverse its direction\n            return current_direction\n        return new_direction'}
